    "The dataset consists of noisy galaxy images paired with probabilistic labels describing morphological features. Each sample includes an image and a corresponding vector of class probabilities, making this a multi-label regression problem.\n",
    "\n",
    "Images and labels are aligned via a galaxy identifier, ensuring consistent mapping between inputs and targets throughout the pipeline."
   ]
