    "id": "Iu57YK7xtSXw"
   },
   "source": [
    "### Data Transformation\n",
    "\n",
    "Data augmentation is applied to increase sample diversity and improve generalization. Random flips, rotations, and jittering simulate different variations in orientation and imaging present in astronomical observations.\n",
    "\n",
    "Images are resized to 224×224 to match the input requirements of the CNN architectures (ResNet-28, LeViT-128s), ensuring consistent training and evaluation across models."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "6Ar0XC0vmNUD"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "batch_size = 8\n",
    "epochs = 10\n",
    "learning_rate = 1e-4\n",
    "n_workers = 2\n",
    "img_size = 224\n",
    "eps = 1e-8 #constant to avoid log divergences"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "vjSa-FNOmNXG"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "resnet_train_transform = transforms.Compose([transforms.Resize((img_size, img_size)), \n",
    "                                             transforms.RandomHorizontalFlip(),\n",
    "                                             transforms.RandomVerticalFlip(),\n",
    "                                             transforms.RandomRotation(30),\n",
    "                                             transforms.ColorJitter(0.1, 0.1, 0.1),\n",
    "                                             transforms.ToTensor()])\n",
    "\n",
    "resnet_val_transform = transforms.Compose([transforms.Resize((img_size, img_size)),\n",
    "                                           transforms.ToTensor()])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "NYehHzR0me5i"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "levit_train_transform = transforms.Compose([transforms.Resize((img_size, img_size)),\n",
    "                                             transforms.RandomHorizontalFlip(),\n",
    "                                             transforms.RandomVerticalFlip(),\n",
    "                                             transforms.RandomRotation(30),\n",
    "                                             transforms.ColorJitter(0.1, 0.1, 0.1),\n",
    "                                             transforms.ToTensor()])\n",
    "\n",
    "levit_val_transform = transforms.Compose([transforms.Resize((img_size, img_size)),\n",
    "                                           transforms.ToTensor()])"
   ]
  },
